data.title: RR Autograph Auction July2012
data.meta_description: RR Autograph Auction July2012 - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. Bid online at www.rrauction.com. Headquartered in Amherst, NH, RR Auction is globally recognized as the trusted source for authentic autographed memorabilia and rare signed documents. Since its inception in 1976, the firm has published over 360 consecutive monthly autograph catalogs, which are distributed internationally. The firm recently auctioned the autographed photo of Albert Einstein with his tongue wagging for a record $74,340 and the check astronaut Neil Armstrong signed the day he left for the moon for $27,350
